description:
In this Sabbath School Lesson, we will study the Bible to see if polygamy is approved by God. There are certain groups of Muslims, Latter Day Saints (Mormons), and Hebrew Israelites who believe that polygamy is an acceptable practice. Additionally, there are many critics of the Bible who claim it cannot be inspired because it reveals the sinful deeds of men and therefore, it is not a holy book. We will address these claims in this lesson.

Lesson Guide: https://www.prophesyagain.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Notes/Polygamy.pdf
